<h2 id="korean-spicy-marinated-tofu"   class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Korean Spicy Marinated Tofu</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer" style="height: 5px;"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;"><strong>Korean Spicy Marinated Tofu</strong> is tofu marinated in a Korean sweet and spicy sauce inspired by the popular <em>Yangnyeom (means spicy sauce</em>) flavor. This recipe is made under 10 minutes and is perfect for vegetarians! </span></div>
